article.description: — Jeremy Sheppard scored 21 points and Ishmael Leggett added 20 as Rhode Island romped past Georgia State 94-59 on Saturday.
article.headline: Sheppard carries Rhode Island past Georgia St. 94-59
article.linkText: Sheppard carries Rhode Island past Georgia St. 94-59
article.story: KINGSTON, R.I. -- — Jeremy Sheppard scored 21 points and Ishmael Leggett added 20 as Rhode Island romped past Georgia State 94-59 on Saturday. Antwan Walker had 13 points for Rhode Island (5-2), which earned its fourth straight home victory. Malik Martin added 12 points. Kane Williams had 19 points for the Panthers (4-2). Jordan Rawls added 14 points.
